
Jahia Source code README
========================

To build the installer :
------------------------

1. install.sh/.bat -P installer

Installer is generated in jahia_pack/package/jahia-installer-package/target/Jahia_xCM*.jar

You can then launch simply using :
java -jar jahia_pack/package/jahia-installer-package/target/Jahia_xCM*.jar

To build and deploy using Maven Jahia Plugin:
---------------------------------------------

1. Copy and customize the settings in jahia/settings.example.xml into your Maven settings.xml file
2. install.sh/.bat
3. deploy.sh/.bat -P LIST_OF_PROFILES_TO_ACTIVATE
4. configure.sh/.bat -P LIST_OF_PROFILES_TO_ACTIVATE

where LIST_OF_PROFILES_TO_ACTIVATE is something like : jahia-tomcat,jahia-mysql
